text: Buyin may refer to: * Buyin, an alternate name of Buin Zahra, a city in Iran * Buyin, Zanjan, a village in Zanjan Province, Iran * BUYIN, a procurement joint-venture by Deutsche Telekom and Orange * "Buy-in", a poker term, see: Glossary of poker terms#buy-in * The purchase of a company by a new manager or management team, see Management buy-in
title: Buyin
